520 float SafeDriveAreaEvaluation::GetOrthogonalAngle(float angle, int SEARCH_LINE_CODE)
521 {
522  int angle_ = 0;
523 
524  if(SEARCH_LINE_CODE == LEFT_TO_MID || SEARCH_LINE_CODE == LEFT_TO_RIGHT || SEARCH_LINE_CODE == MID_TO_RIGHT) angle_ = (angle - 90);
525 
526  if(SEARCH_LINE_CODE == RIGHT_TO_MID || SEARCH_LINE_CODE == RIGHT_TO_LEFT || SEARCH_LINE_CODE == MID_TO_LEFT) angle_ = (angle + 90);
527 
528  if(angle_ > 359) angle_ = angle_ % 360;
529 
530  if(angle_ < 0) angle_ = 360 - abs(angle_);
531 
532  return float(angle_);
